org.jamsim.ascape.weights

Class CategoricalVarWCTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • org.jamsim.ascape.weights.CategoricalVarWCTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel

    public class CategoricalVarWCTableModel
extends AbstractTableModel
    Table Model for the weighting of a categorical variable. Based on an array of MutableNumerators. Modifications to the table model update the numerator of the underlying MutableNumerators.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion

      • CategoricalVarWCTableModel

        public CategoricalVarWCTableModel(MutableNumerator[] values,
                          int displayScaleFactor,
                          double autoAdjustTotal)
        Construct table model with an adjustment factor.
        Parameters:
        values - row values from parameter set
        displayScaleFactor - display scale factor. Values are multiplied by this amount for display only.
        autoAdjustTotal - total used to automatically adjust the last unedited MutableNumerator in a row, or Double.NaN if no adjustment of the last unedited MutableNumerator is to occur. This total is before displayScaleFactor is applied for display.
